_text = "When I look out into the ocean, I see the waves looking back at me.The waves have always been there. They have been in my most vivid memories of my parents and my worst. \n\nWe were surrounded by the ocean for the first 8 years of my life.\n\nAs I look out at this ferry dock, I can't help but let the waves take me away from these memories. I take retreat in them, hiding rather than addressing these emotions face on.\n\nMy memory of them ends here."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MemoryTunnelRoom5, MemoryTunnelRoom5, false)
